    "longBusinessSummary": "Son Ha International Corporation manufactures and trades in household and industrial products in Vietnam and internationally. The company offers supplying new energy products, including solar energy and windy energy; exploiting, trading projects of supplying clean water; and investing in, building, trading projects of industrial real estate. It also provides household appliances, such as electric kettle, rice cooker, and water heater, induction cooker, gas stove, electric water dispenser, water dispensers, stainless steel kitchen sink, cooker hood, RO water filter, hair dryer, blender, plastic water tank, stainless steel water tank, septic tank, and iron. In addition, the company provides industrial stainless-steel pipes, solar system, heat pumps, tanks, and stainless-steel LA products; solar water heaters; and underground and clean water treatment systems. Further, it is involved in the industrial infrastructure; commercial water production and supply services; electricity generation; logistics services; building other civil engineering works; agency, broker, and auctioneer services; and real estate business. It also exports its products. The company was formerly known as SonHa Mechanical Metal Company Ltd. Son Ha International Corporation was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
